snippet.title: Modsix Gaming
snippet.description: Modsix Gaming is my channel for Call of Duty: Mobile content. I served for nearly 10 years as an Airborne Infantry Officer in the United States Army and am an expert in small unit tactics and company/platoon/squad level tactical maneuver. This channel is where I apply that knowledge and expertise to Call of Duty. Inquiries: modsix@amolifiedim.com
